    </li>
    <li id="indonesia_logging" class="flag id">
    <strong>Indonesia - Logging</strong> <a href="http://appgis.dephut.go.id/appgis" target="_blank">Visit</a>
    <p>Logging concessions data represent permit boundaries for selective logging of natural forests in Indonesia.  This dataset is provided by the Indonesia Ministry of Forestry.  This data is available for download from Ministry of Forestry website</p>
